title: Guns N' Roses - Chinese Democracy (Official Single) 10/22/08
description:
It's finally here.  This is the first official single off Axl's new album of the same name, "Chinese Democracy."

I downloaded the official Imeem post of this song and extracted the mp3 audio from the .flv container.  NO TRANSCODING.  This is the highest quality of the song available, probably until the CD drops at the end of November.  I can almost taste the Dr. Pepper!

Though I say quality, it's still just a 128kbps mp3 file.

Enjoy.

-The RiFT
